@startuml

class User {
    -_name: str
    -_email: str
    -_age: int

    +get_name(): str
    +set_name(value: str): void

    +get_email(): str
    +set_email(value: str): void

    +get_age(): int
    +set_age(value: int): void

    +get_info(): str
}

note right of User
Encapsulation:
- Private fields (_name, _email, _age)
- Controlled access via properties

Validation rules:
- name cannot be empty
- email must contain "@"
- age must be >= 0
end note

@enduml
